Invocation Name: engineering words
des:
Ask for Engineering Words, and learn about terms, acronyms, slang, and jargon used in various engineering disciplines.

Engineering Words can help you study and improve your broad knowledge of engineering concepts.

To start, just say "Alexa, launch Engineering Words" or "Alexa, open Engineering Words" to get a word.

At anytime, you can stop by saying "Alexa, stop"

Sponsored by the Engineering Word Of The Day podcast. Produced by Pios Labs. Learn more about the podcast at: http://engineeringwordoftheday.com/
